{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SetFloatBobPhase}}
'''A_FloatBobPhase''' (int ''bob'')

Changes the calling actor's {{c|{{Property|FloatBobPhase}}}} to ''bob'', which takes a number from 0 to 63. If the number is invalid or not in range, the function does nothing.

